               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">GEORGE CLUFF</hi>. I am a silk manufacturer. living in Godfrey-row, Shacklewell-green. On Tuesday evening, the'14th of November, I found the prisoner had left my employ—he was in my employ at that time, but not previous to that—he was working in the room—I found that he was gone, and the coats and other things also—these are part of them.</p>
